		  <td width="135" class="forum_boardrow2" style="border-width: 0px 0px 1px 1px;" valign="top"><div id="messageuser31343823" style="padding-bottom: 2px;"><a href="/profile/Yukariki"><strong>Yukariki</strong></a></div>
		  
		  <a href="/profile/Yukariki"><img src="http://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/useravatars/497699.png" vspace="2" border="0"></a>
		  <br>
		  Offline<br>
		  Joined: Jun 2011<br>
